name: Service_Value_Analytics_tp
label: Service Value Analytics
description: Take a business, KPI-led view of how your Service users interact with your customer data.  Understand what components on the page are used by high-productivity users, and what unused components may be beneficial to users who are still learning.

title.label: What is the sequence of clicks on page components?
title.subtitleLabel: How long does it take to complete the next action?

title.label: When and Where do users navigate about the app?
What is the last component a user interacts with before leaving their session?
Where and When do users typically end their session?

content.description: Each bubble represents the sum of measures for cases owned by [Owner.Name]. The total time to complete actions on their cases was [sum_Interactions.SUMTimeToAction] seconds, over a total of [sum_Interactions.TotalClicks] clicks. The total age of their cases is [sum_Age], spread across [unique_Id] cases,  [sum_Interactions.UniqueSessionKey] sessions. Total time spent waiting after performing these actions is [sum_Interactions.SumStallTime] seconds. Finally, a total of [sum_Interactions.UniqueUserCount] users interacted with their cases.
